 SIMPLE PROGRAMS:
1.	Write a C program that contains a string (char pointer) with a value ‘Hello world’. The program should AND or and XOR each character in this string with 127 and display the result.
2.	Write a Java program to implement the DES algorithm logic.
3.	Write a C/JAVA program to implement the Rijndael algorithm logic.
4.	Write a Java program to implement RSA Algorithm.
5.	Calculate the message digest of a text using the SHA-1 algorithm in JAVA.
6.	Calculate the message digest of a text using the MD5 algorithm in JAVA


